data.description: WOW! Check out this amazing opportunity right by the heart of the UT campus! All major items are only 3 years old! Newers include; Roof, Furnace and AC, Water Heater, Breaker Box, Glass Block Basement Windows, 2 Car Garage, and Concrete Driveway. Full basement that is ready to be finished and could also provide a massive amount of storage space. Fresh paint throughout, remodeled bathroom with marble tile surround, and brand new carpet in all of the bedrooms, make this one truly TURN KEY. Call to schedule your private showing today!!
